98% sugar free formula with echinacea, zinc and a boost of vitamin C to reduce the severity and duration of common cold symptoms. Cold + Flu

Blackmores Bio C® 1000 + Effervescent is a 98% sugar free formula with echinacea, Zinc and a boost of viamin C to support immune system health and reduce the severity and duration of common cold symptoms.

 

A great tasting, easy to take high potency one-a-day dose of vitamin C sweetened with naturally derived ingredients.

Contains echinacea & zinc

Reduces the severity and duration of common colds symptoms

98% sugar free and great tasting orange flavour

Supports immune system health

Supports general health and wellbeing

Vitamin C and zinc are antioxidants and help reduce free radicals formed in the body
